name: Toys
description: The Artist and Lead guitarist Kurt S. of the Nip Drivers on a wild night in Los Angeles. Skid row buildings were being bought up by Chinese toy importers and the neon toys signs down those derelict streets was surreal. Los Feliz is juxtaposed with downtown LA to capture the feeling of high movement. This is an acrylic painting, one of my earliest works. The painting is sold to a buyer in NYC. Provenance: Shown in LA.
